original_title: Songs from the compost: mutating bodies, imploding stars
overview: Made in collaboration with Marija Olšauskaitė and Julija Lukas Steponaitytė, Songs from the compost is a hypnotic exploration of nonhuman forms of consciousness and different dimensions of symbiotic life: interdependence, surrender, death, and decay. [Overview Courtesy of Canal Projects]
title: Songs from the compost: mutating bodies, imploding stars
